"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"蒋经国70岁时，在日记里回忆他小时候背诵的格言：登天难，求人更难；黄连苦，贫穷更苦；春冰薄，人情更薄；江湖险，人心更险。知其难，甘其苦，耐其薄，测其险，可以处世矣，可以应变矣。蒋经国说：这格言说的是人性之恶，但人性也有光明一面。人性本善，但往往为恶所蔽，为政之道，就在于启发善根！\",\"timestamp\":1642169812,\"title\":\"为政之道，就在于启发善根\"},\"digest\":\"GDLU8kgEMbA5ZfU0TQ8YbV_aD6rG8N93OoypU_BlSmo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x12e874169A42b20E15d4BE9d799e6c01E79b48D6\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ywp8GA5U63bfPCNZsGTGVHO7K4chXlTnJnG56TGpACA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"g3zuvil2osQ0q7dGBYxMGUzbmXuHrOb6SSVa3zHmr4g\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"hEP850i4B0XhFcjV0Uof2AE2Mcn8t_WnbTVnVI5SI1oygh5YIiV6mj-riZdM8thdRDmjL3nDxn8t4SvHXgGwaA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3e6734e7f4490b1e9c88a48e23e8509d38bfb93c96dfab504bd7bc6dbd9c73144675e8e1b0580b97fd7323c063455c27c617448b6fc28d213a40d8fcaf643e441b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Ywp8GA5U63bfPCNZsGTGVHO7K4chXlTnJnG56TGpACA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"g3zuvil2osQ0q7dGBYxMGUzbmXuHrOb6SSVa3zHmr4g\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"GDLU8kgEMbA5ZfU0TQ8YbV_aD6rG8N93OoypU_BlSmo\"}"